'''Louise Archer''' (born 1973) is [[Karl Mannheim]] Professor of Sociology of Education at the [[University College London]] [[UCL Institute of Education|Institute of Education]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ucl.ac.uk/ioe/news-events/news-pub/eps-news/eps-louise-archer-karl-mannheim-chair|title=Professor Louise Archer appointed to the Karl Mannheim Chair|website=Ucl.ac.uk|accessdate=18 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ucl.ac.uk/ioe/about/ioe-life/academics/louise-archer|title=Louise Archer|website=Ucl.ac.uk|accessdate=18 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://iris.ucl.ac.uk/iris/browse/profile?upi=LARCH93|title=Iris View Profile|website=Iris.ucl.ac.uk|accessdate=18 October 2017}}</ref>

